  "body": "Performance >>>>>>>>> Looks\n\n\n### 👋 Hello, Welcome To Heavy Optimized  \nExperience unparalleled performance with our Heavy Optimized modpack, designed to squeeze every ounce of FPS out of your computer. This modpack prioritizes optimization, ensuring smooth gameplay even on lower-end machines by dialing back some visual elements. Say goodbye to lag and hello to buttery smooth performance, perfect for those who value gameplay fluidity over aesthetics. Whether you have a high-end gaming rig or a modest setup, Heavy Optimized ensures you get the best performance possible.\n\n### 🔧 Compatibility  \nI made this modpack to maximize performance, even if it means sacrificing some visual quality. You can still add other mods to the pack if you wish, but be mindful of potential effects on performance.\n\n### ⚙️ How Fast Does This Modpack Update?  \nI commit to keeping Heavy Optimized up-to-date. I roll out updates as soon as possible to ensure you always have the best optimization. Even if I can’t update all mods, we release versions that offer the highest performance within a few days of any major updates.\n\n\nbanner :)\n![Banner](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/166569fccaa1b684891d2dcb99478328f2f6929f.png)",
